cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on wireless communication systems, specifically small cell wireless systems aided by unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of UAVs also suggests a potential connection to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
